                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5208" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0099</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8273 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新城投公司抗疫复工中的风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Risk Management In XINCHENG&#39;s Anti- COVID-19-epidemic And Resumption Of Work</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘建利，赵金煜，周霞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京建筑大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京市房山新城置业有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工程项目风险；风险损失；风险应对策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">project risk; risk loss; risk response strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了北京市房山区新城投资有限公司2020年遭遇新冠疫情巨大冲击，其承担的北京市最大的棚改项目（长阳0607棚改项目）快速反应，实施积极的风险管理，实现稳步复工的历程。长阳0607 棚改项目是北京市和房山区的重点民生工程，新城投资公司高度重视，疫情一出，立即多方搜集信息，预判可能出现的各种风险，在风险分析的基础上通过风险阻断、风险预防、风险减轻等积极的应对措施，对疫情造成的进度延误和成本上升予以控制，降低了疫情风险对项目的影响。由于风险管控及时到位，疫情防控工作扎实有效，这一涉及9个开工地块、4000多名施工人员的大型项目工程在三个月内恢复计划进度，同时，其出色的工作受到北京市住房和城乡建设委员会发布的《关于对新冠肺炎疫情防控期间复工返岗工作表现突出的工程参建单位给与表扬的通报》通报表扬。本案例旨在通过对新城投公司疫情期间风险管理操作的复盘，让学生对工程项目风险有全面理解，掌握工程项目风险管理的过程和要点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> This case describes the process in which Beijing Fangshan District Xincheng Investment Co., Ltd. undertook controlled risks of coVID-19, and resumed work steadily in Changyang 0607 Shantytown Reform project, which is the key livelihood project in Beijing and Fangshan district. Because Changyang 0607 Shantytown Reform Project is the largest shantytown reform project in Beijing, it attaches great importance to Xincheng investment co., LTD. When the coVID-19 epidemic broke out，Xincheng investment co., LTD immediately collected information, anticipated possible risks. Through risk blocking, risk prevention, risk mitigation, active coping measures, such as the outbreak caused by schedule delays and cost rise to control, reduce the risk of the project. Because of the effective disease prevention and control work, the large project involved nine blocks, more than 4000 workers, didn’t delay construction schedule. At the same time, its excellent risk management is praised by Beijing housing and urban and rural construction committee. This case aims to enable students to have a comprehensive understanding of the engineering project risks, and to master the process and key points of risk management of engineering projects through the review of the risk management operation of Xincheng Investment co., LTD.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《工程项目管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理流程；风险评估与分担；风险应对策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
